is there a government agency to protect investors? The Securities and Exchange Commission (SEC) is a government agency that protects investors.
Which age group has the highest global HIV/AIDS death rate? The highest global HIV/AIDS death rate is in the age group 15-24.

Which food commodity is raising as income and urbanization raise? As income and urbanization raise, the price of food commodities that are considered "luxury" items, such as meats and cheeses, will also rise.
Which naturally occurring form is silicon the most commonly found in? Silicon is the most commonly found form of silicon dioxide.
silicon is commonly found in which naturally occurring form? Silicon is found in its elemental form in nature.
is silicon found in fluoride? Fluoride is a compound that contains the element fluorine. Silicon is a chemical element with the symbol Si and atomic number 14. Silicon is not found in fluoride.
is silicon found in sulfide? Silicon is not found in sulfide.
is silicon found in oxide? Silicon dioxide (SiO2) is the most common oxide of silicon.
is silicon found in metallic element? Silicon is not a metallic element.
